ZH: 我们的业障来自以往的恶行。
EN: Our karmic obstacles come from past misdeeds.

ZH: 修行可以减轻业障。
EN: Practice can lessen karmic obstacles.

ZH: 禅坐可以帮助我们清除业障。
EN: Meditation can help us clear karmic obstacles.

ZH: 每个人都有不同的业障。
EN: Everyone has different karmic obstacles.

ZH: 通过修行可以解脱业障。
EN: Through practice, we can overcome karmic obstacles.

ZH: 业障可以在未来生命中产生影响。
EN: Karmic obstacles can have an impact in future lives.

ZH: 忏悔可以减轻业障。
EN: Repentance can lessen karmic obstacles.

ZH: 用心修行可以消除业障。
EN: Diligent practice can eliminate karmic obstacles.

ZH: 我们要不断努力消除自己的业障。
EN: We must continuously strive to eliminate our own karmic obstacles.

ZH: 业障是我们修行的阻碍。
EN: Karmic obstacles are hindrances to our practice.

ZH: 业障的根源来自过去的恶行。
EN: The root of karmic obstacles lies in past misdeeds.

ZH: 念经可以帮助减轻业障。
EN: Reciting sutras can help lessen karmic obstacles.

ZH: 善行可以减少业障的累积。
EN: Good deeds can reduce the accumulation of karmic obstacles.

ZH: 我们应该诚心悔过以消除业障。
EN: We should sincerely repent to eliminate karmic obstacles.

ZH: 业障是因果循环的一部分。
EN: Karmic obstacles are part of the cycle of cause and effect.

ZH: 心地纯净可以减轻业障的影响。
EN: Having a pure heart can lessen the impact of karmic obstacles.

ZH: 业障会随着修行的深入而逐渐消失。
EN: Karmic obstacles will gradually disappear as practice deepens.

ZH: 只有修行才能超越业障的束缚。
EN: Only through practice can we transcend the shackles of karmic obstacles.

ZH: 觉悟可以帮助我们了解业障的本质。
EN: Awakening can help us understand the nature of karmic obstacles.

ZH: 善念可以减少业障的产生。
EN: Cultivating wholesome thoughts can reduce the arising of karmic obstacles.
